WEBVTT

00:06:28.920 --> 00:06:32.069
I said, "Ten times less?
Is it because of my English?"

00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:36.090
He said, "Not your English. 
Your this ... skin."

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:41.009
For the first time in my life,
someone had told me I was less than him.

00:06:41.009 --> 00:06:44.239
I have faced a lot of challenges in life,
and I could take on more,

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:46.119
but to challenge my skin?

00:06:46.120 --> 00:06:47.440
This was a very big thing.

00:06:48.640 --> 00:06:51.120
I always carry this picture in my wallet.

00:06:51.230 --> 00:06:56.315
(Applause)

00:06:56.315 --> 00:07:02.655
My color ... my color comes from them.
This is my biggest heritage.